name: Tactical Re-Call (V)
Lore: 'Sophisticated communication equipment hidden in the ruins of the extinct Massassi race is used to coordinate forces and to re-call Rebel officers for debriefing and orders.',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to deploy on opponent''s site. Target opponent''s leader at a site or character at the Galactic Senate. Target''s game text is canceled. Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.',
